name: 艾伦·拉塔-莫莉塞特
name_full: 艾伦·拉塔-莫莉塞特 Aaron Latta-Morissette

last_movies.title: 帝王计划：怪兽遗产 第一季

introduction: Aaron Latta-Morissette is an American actor born to Susan Morissette, a sign-language interpreter, and Darlene Latta, a psycho-therapist. He and his older brother were raised Jewish in Rehoboth Beach, Delaware. After finding his voice in the high school theatre program, Aaron soon began his formal training in New York City and found a mentor-ship in his acting coach, Matthew James Thomas. Through his time at the William Esper Studio, The Drama League, and The PIT, he has continually been pushed to re-evaluate the world, his work, and himself.
